{"title":"打麦歌","authors":[],"dates":[{"year":1959,"month":6,"day":18}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"打麦歌"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"严阵满树青桃红了嘴，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"熟透了的杏子落成堆，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"谁去理会？"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"打麦忙得火烧眉。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"场上的人儿排成了队，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"好似龙摆尾，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"?耞落地珍珠滚，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"?耞起似莺乱飞。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"打了一场一场又一场，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"场场珠宝乱碰腿，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"打这样的场呵，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"多有滋味："},{"type":"paragraph","text":"看着眼前的金堆银堆，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"人人都笑歪了嘴，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"身上的暑热呵，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"何用轻风来吹！"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":8,"page_end":8}